categories: Category:Imperial Army officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: This female individual served as the commander of a Imperial garrison stationed at an Imperial installation on Eadu in 0 BBY. When Director Orson Krennic arrived at the facility to discover which of the scientists stationed on Eadu had conspired with a pilot to send messages to the Rebellion, the garrison commander stepped forward to offer a welcome to Krennic but was waved off by the director as he had no interest in delaying what he had arrived to do.
